Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:32.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}时间不会停留
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:39.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}心愿被风吹散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:44.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}喉咙干涩沙哑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:48.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不知前方有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:51.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你我就像一组平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:54.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坚强的你从不回头
